&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Minno&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minno is a global media and technology company based in Nashville, Tennessee, on a mission to help kids and families experience Jesus every day through media and technology.&lt;/p&gt;
